    <briefdescription>
<para>Wrapper to allow a single conversion to another type. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>For example</para>
<para>Conversion from Hz to Mhz can be achieved by defining</para>
<para>using FrequencyHzToMHz = <ref refid="structStrongTypeConversion" kindref="compound">StrongTypeConversion&lt;FrequencyMHz, FrequencyHz, 1, 1000000&gt;</ref>;</para>
<para>Then</para>
<para>FrequencyHz hz(1000000); FrequencyHz mhz = HzToMHz(hz);</para>
<para>Would give mhz = 1. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
